Movie Recommendation System Using Content-Based Filtering

Project Overview

This project implements a simple movie recommendation system using the Content-Based Filtering technique. The system recommends movies to users based on the genres of their favorite movie. By comparing movie genres, it suggests similar movies that match the user's interests.

Features

- Recommends movies based on user preferences
- Uses Content-Based Filtering
- Simple and beginner-friendly Python implementation
- Easy to modify and extend with more movies and genres

Technologies Used

- Python 3

How It Works

1. The user enters their favorite movie.
2. The system identifies the genres of the selected movie.
3. It compares these genres with other movies in the dataset.
4. Movies with similar genres are recommended to the user.

